{"tid":986121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到處威脅國中小女生「一起上廁所」　31歲變態男落網","createTime":"2019-01-18T07:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:26:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b26564631cca9685bd42b4e87469526881aa3eb","tid":986121,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peLZ5kQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeLZ5kQ.png&h=b788bc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本東京出現一名變態狼，到處找國中小女學生「一起去廁所」！<br />\n <br />\n根據《日テレNEWS》報導，東京都日野市車站內，一女子中學生在月台上突遭一名陌生男子威脅「跟我一起去廁所」，正當女學生覺得害怕想打給媽媽求救時，陌生男子更出聲恐嚇「敢打電話就打妳！」，所幸女學生最後順利脫逃。<br />\n <br />\n警方循線找到這名叫做中島的31歲嫌犯，雖然中島否認犯行，但近來東京都內傳出有不少國中小女學生遭陌生男子威脅「一起去廁所」，警方正在調查是否都是同一人犯案。"},{"pid":"2de098983849af0b734abcb700b6b8a1f06b0d39","tid":986121,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"怕廁所有怪叔叔先搵人陪姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76805e4b00df7eda5116a91b3f0143f33b1ccfd4","tid":986121,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"個樣生到咁係壓力大咗d㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e27002ae388fa1de8badb2be6c0ebfe22c0ec4","tid":986121,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"廁所保鏢 行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}